---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
  title="Cortex Team Stack — AI Trained on Your Brand DNA | Fast Web Guru"
  description="Cortex Team Stack builds your Business DNA and trains a personalised AI brain on your brand. Plus 1 hr/mo real AI Specialist review. Part of Cortex ($30/mo). Works on any website."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="section-dark py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
        <span class="chip">Cortex Team Stack</span>
        <span class="chip-inverse">$10/month</span>
        <span class="chip-inverse">Part of Cortex — $30/month total</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-zinc-300">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">›</span>
        <a href="/cortex" class="hover:text-zinc-300">Cortex AI</a>
        <span class="mx-2">›</span>
        <span class="text-zinc-400">Team Stack</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-white mb-6">AI that actually knows your business.</h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">Cortex Team Stack builds your Business DNA — your brand ingested and trained into a personalised AI brain. Every output it produces sounds like you, because it was built from you. Plus 1 hour a month of a real AI Specialist who reviews every output before it touches your brand.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="/#assessment" class="btn-primary text-base py-4 px-8">Add Cortex to Your Website — $30/Month</a>
        <a href="/#assessment" class="btn-ghost-inverse text-base py-4">Or get a free AI assessment first →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM -->
  <section class="section-warm py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-6">Generic AI sounds like every other business.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>You open an AI tool. You ask it to write something for your business. It does — and it sounds perfectly fine. It also sounds exactly like your competitor's content, and the content of every other business who used the same tool with a similar prompt.</p>
        <p>That's not a prompt problem. It's a training problem.</p>
        <p>Generic AI has read the entire internet. None of it is specifically about your brand, your products, your tone of voice, or what your customers actually respond to.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-dark font-semibold">Cortex Team Stack fixes this at the foundation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION -->
  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-6">Your business, ingested. Your AI, personalised.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">Cortex Team Stack starts with the Business DNA Workshop — a short onboarding session where your AI Specialist gathers your existing documents:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 list-none p-0 mb-8">
        {[
          'Your product catalogue and descriptions',
          'Past copy and content that represents your voice',
          'Style guides, brand notes, or tone of voice documents',
          'Key customer language and phrases your audience uses',
          'Anything else that defines how your business communicates',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
            <span class="text-brand-text-secondary">{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">From these, we build your <strong class="text-brand-dark">Brand DNA</strong> — a structured document that captures your brand in a format the AI understands.</p>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">This powers your <strong class="text-brand-dark">Digital Marketing Brain</strong> — a personalised AI instance trained on your Business DNA and nothing else. When it generates content, it generates it for your business. Not for a generic placeholder company.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE AI SPECIALIST -->
  <section class="section-mid section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-6">A real human reviews every output. Every month.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">Your 1 hour per month of AI Specialist time is with a real person — not a chatbot, not an automated checker.</p>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        {[
          'Reviews your Cortex outputs before they reach your brand',
          'Refines your Brand DNA as your business evolves',
          'Prepares data, documents, and inputs for your workflows each month',
          'Flags when the AI has drifted from your voice and corrects it',
          'Acts as your quality controller for everything Cortex produces',
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
            <p class="text-brand-text-secondary">{item}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="callout-box mt-10">
        <p class="text-brand-dark font-medium">This is what separates Cortex Team Stack from any other AI tool. The AI generates at speed; the specialist makes sure it's actually right for your brand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="mb-12">What Team Stack gives you</h2>
      <div class="space-y-10">
        {[
          { title: 'Business DNA Workshop', body: 'A 45-minute onboarding session to gather your documents and build your Brand DNA file. Happens in Week 1. Your AI brain is live within 7 days of signing up.' },
          { title: 'Your Brand DNA file', body: 'A structured, portable document that captures your brand for the AI. Yours to keep — load it into any AI tool you use. Updated by your AI Specialist as your business evolves.' },
          { title: 'Your Digital Marketing Brain', body: 'A personalised AI instance trained only on your Brand DNA. Use it for content, copy, marketing strategy, email drafts, social posts, product descriptions — outputs that sound like your business, not generic AI.' },
          { title: 'AI Specialist — 1 hour/month', body: 'A real person. Reviews, refines, prepares. Your quality controller for the AI layer. Included every month.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex gap-5 pb-10 border-b border-brand-border last:border-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THIS IS PART OF CORTEX -->
  <section class="section-warm py-14">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Team Stack is one of three Cortex pillars.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary mb-8">Cortex Team Stack is $10/month — part of Cortex, the $30/month AI ecosystem. Your Business DNA from Team Stack is what powers the workflows in Ops Grid. The three pillars aren't independent — they compound.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <a href="/cortex/host-systems" class="bg-brand-surface-mid border border-brand-border rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-brand-accent transition-colors">
          <p class="font-bold mb-1">Cortex Host Systems ($10)</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary">AI-native hosting. Talk-to-Edit.</p>
          <p class="text-brand-accent text-xs mt-2">Learn more →</p>
        </a>
        <div class="bg-brand-accent rounded-lg p-5 text-brand-dark">
          <p class="font-bold mb-1">Cortex Team Stack ($10)</p>
          <p class="text-sm">This pillar. Business DNA + AI brain + Specialist.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/cortex/ops-grid" class="bg-brand-surface-mid border border-brand-border rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-brand-accent transition-colors">
          <p class="font-bold mb-1">Cortex Ops Grid ($10)</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary">20 bespoke growth workflows to work through with your team — more added regularly.</p>
          <p class="text-brand-accent text-xs mt-2">Learn more →</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <a href="/cortex" class="btn-ghost">See the full Cortex page →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIAL -->
  <section class="section-dark py-12">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <figure class="text-center">
        <blockquote class="text-xl text-zinc-200 italic leading-relaxed mb-4">
          "I've tried three different AI tools and they all wrote the same generic rubbish. Cortex actually sounds like us. That alone is worth the $30."
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">— [Client name], [Business type], [City] <span class="text-zinc-600">[Testimonial to be confirmed]</span></figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="mb-6">Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-lg mb-8"><strong>Cortex — $30/month</strong> (Team Stack included)<br/>Or add Cortex to FWG Core hosting: <strong>$70/month total</strong></p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
        <a href="/#assessment" class="btn-primary">Add Cortex to Your Website — $30/Month</a>
        <a href="/#assessment" class="btn-ghost">Or: Get Your Free AI Assessment →</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Month-to-month. No setup fee. Cancel anytime. Works on any website, any host.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
